{"tid":1034563,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"一人N首醫神無派台嘅深度歌","createTime":"2019-02-24T04:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T04:23:29.000Z","uid":33259,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7955f227f11511586a42c5a73b647584000eb92e","tid":1034563,"uid":33259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"醫神把聲本身已經好有穿透力 聲厚音闊感情聲質有層次<br />\n好多歌詞意思由佢唱出黎到可以入心入肺 好多深刻反省<br />\n小弟聽咗十幾年醫神 人生唔同時段聽每隻歌都有唔同味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分享下最深刻嘅歌：<br />\n《天公地道》- 首歌從一個好客觀嘅角度出發描述人生各種際遇。第一次聽已經覺得好深，人生遇到種種不順景，迷失，又再搵到方向，隻歌就陪住我呢十年嘅人生起跌，每次人生轉折之後聽又有一翻領悟同體會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8mHOlL1WRvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8mHOlL1WRvs&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=ba852375\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8mHOlL1WRvs</a><br />\n仲有好多首呢類嘅歌 巴打們應該都有好多故事講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如大家一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e17fc6a57428c739a0cc470f7a0ddb79e9b3374","tid":1034563,"uid":200270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"白玫瑰好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然唔記得有冇派過台"}]}